reviewText: Excellent!! Best painting instruction brush techniques!!!
Very helpful and detailed.  Been painting for many years and learned many new techniques.

I like how he paints roses and other flowers.  This book shows his technique and is a good learning tool with many excellent tips and ideas.  There are lots of pictures and fairly good explanations.  While the flowers are more stylized than realistic, his art work is beautiful.  As with most things, practice, practice, practice is the key to success and Mr. Jenkins is proof of such success.
